---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <section class="pt-40 pb-32 sm:pb-40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-12 gap-8 sm:gap-16">
        <div class="sm:col-span-5">
          <p class="reveal visible text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-white/30 uppercase">Services</p>
          <h1 class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1 mt-6 text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] leading-tight text-white">
            Ce que je<br />
            <span class="italic text-gradient-ember">propose</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2 mt-6 w-16 h-0.5 bg-amber-500/50" />
          <p class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2 mt-6 text-base text-white/40 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            Du site vitrine à l'application complexe, chaque projet est unique. Voici comment je peux vous aider.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-6 sm:col-start-7 space-y-12">
          <div class="reveal visible">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <span class="text-5xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] text-white/10 leading-none shrink-0">01</span>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-white">WordPress</h2>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
                  Thème sur mesure, WooCommerce, plugins. Je construis chaque site depuis zéro, 
                  pas de template pré-fait. Design sur mesure, performance optimisée, maintenance incluse.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Thème sur mesure</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">WooCommerce</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Performance</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <span class="text-5xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] text-white/10 leading-none shrink-0">02</span>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-white">Développement sur mesure</h2>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
                  Next.js, Astro, React, Node.js. Des sites statiques ultra-rapides aux applications dynamiques.
                  Stack moderne, déploiement continu via Git, hébergement sur Vercel.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Next.js / Astro</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">React / TypeScript</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Vercel</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <span class="text-5xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] text-white/10 leading-none shrink-0">03</span>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-white">Maintenance & Évolution</h2>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
                  Audit technique, mises à jour de sécurité, amélioration des performances.
                  Je reprends aussi des sites existants pour les moderniser.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Audit & Sécurité</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Migration</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white/40">Performance</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative border-t border-white/5 py-32 sm:py-40 bg-deep-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="reveal text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] leading-tight text-white">
          Vous ne savez pas par où commencer ?
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1 mt-4 text-base text-white/40">
          C'est normal. On en parle 30 minutes sans engagement. Vous repartez avec une vision claire.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-deep-900 text-sm font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-amber-400 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/20">
          Réserver un appel
          <span>→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
